<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>You're In | InboxGlobal</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #0B0F1A;
      color: #E2E8F0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -40%;
      left: -20%;
      width: 80%;
      height: 80%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(34,211,238,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -30%;
      right: -10%;
      width: 60%;
      height: 60%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(167,139,250,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 560px;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #22D3EE;
      background: rgba(34,211,238,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,0.2);
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #94A3B8;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #111827;
      border: 1px solid #1E293B;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .card-label {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #64748B;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .step:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .step-num {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #22D3EE;
      background: rgba(34,211,238,0.1);
      min-width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 6px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .step-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #CBD5E1;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .step-text strong {
      color: #E2E8F0;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .note {
      background: rgba(167,139,250,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(167,139,250,0.15);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .note p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #94A3B8;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .note strong {
      color: #A78BFA;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 8px;
    }

    .footer-brand {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #E2E8F0;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .footer-tag {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #475569;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      h1 { font-size: 28px; }
      .card { padding: 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="badge">Purchase Confirmed</div>
    <h1>You're in. Here's what happens next.</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Your access to the Outbound Ops Standard is on its way. Everything you need arrives by email within the next few minutes.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-label">Next Steps</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Check your inbox.</strong> You will receive an email from InboxGlobal with your access link. If it does not appear within 5 minutes, check spam or promotions.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Open the Notion link.</strong> Click Duplicate to copy the full Ops Standard into your own Notion workspace.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Start with the 30-Day Onboarding.</strong> Week 1 maps your system. Every day has a defined output so you always know what to do next.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      <p><strong>Need help?</strong> Reply directly to the access email. You will reach a real operator, not a support queue.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-brand">InboxGlobal</div>
      <div class="footer-tag">SYSTEM INTEGRITY FOR OUTBOUND</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
